Title: The Reckoning
Plot: Allison dreams about hitting a girl with her car and a woman who's house is haunted. She finds out that the woman killed herself. Now Allison is trying to put all the pieces together.
GuestStars: Keith Oney, Paige Hurd, Cortney Keim, Lawrence Monoson, Suki Kaiser, Amanda Thorp, Katie Cecil, Holliston Coleman
